    "Therefore, in this section, we conduct a series of tests on the generalization capabilities of knowledgedriven agents within the framework to examine whether LLMs can learn knowledge from experiential fragments and apply it to different scenarios.1) Altering the number of lanes on the main roadway: Initially, we conducted tests with minor variations in scenario complexity by changing the number of lanes on the merging main roadway.",
